query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(mk t mi_idx) */ select min(mi_idx.info) AS rating,
min(t.title) AS movie_title
from title AS t
inner join movie_keyword AS mk
on t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.production_year < 2013
inner join movie_info_idx AS mi_idx
on mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi_idx.info > '3.0';
